    <body>
        <div class="jumbotron text-center bg-transparent">
            <h1 class="display-4" style="margin-top: 15%">Rexom <i style="color: rgb(233, 30, 99);" class="fas fa-music"></i></h1>
            <p class="lead display-6">Give your server a <b style="color: rgb(233, 30, 99);">tune.</b></p>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" onclick="location.href='https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?response_type=code&client_id=<%= bot.user.id %>&permissions=6747975000&redirect_uri=<%= collback %>&scope=bot%20applications.commands'">Invite</button>
            <% if (user && user.id) {%>
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg" onclick="location.href='/dashboard'">Dashboard</button>
                <% } else {%>
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg" onclick="location.href='/login'">Login</button>
                    <% } %>

                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center head" style="color: black">
                            <h1><b>Give your server a <b style="color: rgb(233, 30, 99);">tune.</b></b>
                            </h1>
                        </div>
                        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center subtext" style="color: black">
                            <p>Music bots are always what gives an artistic touch to servers, but Rexom gives a different touch.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="container pt-10 custom-2">
                            <img src="https://cdn.wallpapersafari.com/88/15/QV8zlt.jpg">
                            <h3><b style="color: rgba(249,99,0,255);">Music</b> <b style="color: rgba(12,217,90,255);">Support.</b></h3>
                            <p style="color: black">
                                rexom features support for all song playback sites such as spotify soundcloud and more
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="container pt-16 custom-1">
                            <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/898309437486424095/901593150093668413/unknown.png">
                            <h3><b style="color: rgba(249,99,0,255);">Easy </b><b style="color: rgb(233, 30, 99);">to</b><b style="color: rgba(12,217,90,255);"> Setting.</b></h3>
                            <p style="color: black">
                                This is the first music bot that supports both Arabic and English, and like any other bot, it supports changing the prefix and adjusting DJ rank settings.
                            </p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="container pt-10 custom-2">
                            <img src="https://media.discordapp.net/attachments/898309437486424095/901592550475968522/unknown.png?width=911&height=498">
                            <h3><b style="color: rgb(241, 196, 15);">Slash Commands</b> <b style="color: rgb(233, 30, 99);">and</b> <b style="color: rgb(52, 152, 219);">Get Context</b></h3>
                            <p style="color: black">
                                Support all new Discord updates like slash command, get context, buttons, and more, better features and updates coming in.
                            </p>
                        </div>
    </body>
    <footer>
        <div class="d-flex flex-row-reverse bd-highlight ng-dark" style="margin-top: 20%" align="center">
        </div>
